# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Crucible — public repository ignore rules
# Keep the product surface tracked; keep local harness noise and secrets out.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Build & package artifacts ---
/target/
**/target/
Cargo.lock.bak
dist/
*.rlib
*.rmeta

# --- Mutation / coverage / profiling (generated) ---
/mutants.out/
/mutants.out.old/
**/mutants.out/
**/mutants.out.old/
*.profraw
*.profdata
coverage/
.htmlcov/
lcov.info
**/lcov.info
*.lcov

# Proof-crate local builds (source + captured mutants output stay committed)
examples/proof/**/target/
examples/proof/**/mutants.out/
examples/proof/**/Cargo.lock

# Crucible runtime output (never commit)
**/.crucible/survivors.json
**/.crucible/receipts/
**/.crucible/*.receipt

# --- OS & editors ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
*.swo
*.orig
*.rej
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
*.sublime-*

# --- Local agent / IDE harness state (never ship) ---
# Product plugin manifests stay tracked: .claude-plugin/, .codex-plugin/
.claude/
.grok/
.agents/
.agent/
.cursor/
.codex/
.gemini/
.windsurf/
.continue/
.aider*
.repomix*
.worktrees/
.grove/
.summoner/
.augment/
.github/copilot-instructions.local.md

# --- Env, secrets, local overrides ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
credentials.*
secrets.*
*.local
*.local.*
!.env.example

# --- Internal planning (not the product docs under docs/*.md) ---
docs/internal/
**/TODO.local.md
**/NOTES.local.md
**/scratch/
**/tmp/
/tmp/

# --- Logs & misc local noise ---
*.log
logs/
.cache/
.direnv/
.direnv
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# Self-harden debug log (scripts/mutate-diff may write this)
**/last-mutants.log
target/last-mutants.log
examples/demo/.git/
